00:12:57,140 --> 00:12:59,460
Cik Wei, saya hantar awak balik.

263
00:13:12,980 --> 00:13:14,340
Jangan panggil saya Cik Wei.

264
00:13:16,740 --> 00:13:17,820
Panggil nama saya.

265
00:13:19,780 --> 00:13:21,620
Ya... Yahan.

266
00:13:23,380 --> 00:13:28,300
Cakaplah. Tidakkah saya cantik?

267
00:13:31,540 --> 00:13:33,140
Tidakkah saya cemerlang?

268
00:13:38,780 --> 00:13:40,700
Tidakkah saya layak disukai?

269
00:13:43,220 --> 00:13:44,260
Awak cantik.

270
00:13:49,540 --> 00:13:51,140
Adakah awak sukai saya?

271
00:13:52,580 --> 00:13:53,340
Saya...

272
00:13:56,340 --> 00:13:57,580
Adakah awak berani mencium saya?

273
00:13:59,260 --> 00:14:00,260
Ini tak sesuai.

274
00:14:06,020 --> 00:14:07,700
Inginkah awak mencium saya?

275
00:14:34,020 --> 00:14:35,580
Bolehkah awak perlahan-lahan?

276
00:14:39,500 --> 00:14:40,500
Awak buat apa?

277
00:14:40,700 --> 00:14:41,740
Adakah awak dah gila?

278
00:14:41,980 --> 00:14:43,620
Ya. Saya marah sampai gila.

279
00:14:43,820 --> 00:14:44,940
Awak sedang buat apa?

280
00:14:45,100 --> 00:14:45,460
Saya...

281
00:14:45,460 --> 00:14:46,100
Bukankah awak

282
00:14:46,100 --> 00:14:46,940
tak pernah diserang?

283
00:14:46,940 --> 00:14:47,500
Mengapa awak tak lindungi diri

284
00:14:47,500 --> 00:14:48,660
pada waktu yang cemas?

285
00:14:48,900 --> 00:14:50,060
Bukankah awak hebat?

286
00:14:50,060 --> 00:14:50,820
Awak boleh pukul dia, marahi dia

287
00:14:50,820 --> 00:14:51,740
dan tolak tangannya.

288
00:14:51,740 --> 00:14:53,260
Awak ingat saya mahu minum bersamanya?

289
00:14:53,580 --> 00:14:53,980
Sebab dia

290
00:14:53,980 --> 00:14:54,420
ialah klien penting

291
00:14:54,420 --> 00:14:55,700
untuk syarikat kita.

292
00:14:56,140 --> 00:14:58,180
Ya. Dia klien syarikat kita.

293
00:14:59,100 --> 00:15:00,140
Namun, mulai esok,

294
00:15:00,140 --> 00:15:00,580
saya akan hentikan

295
00:15:00,580 --> 00:15:01,700
semua kerjasama dengan mereka.

296
00:15:02,140 --> 00:15:02,900
Adakah awak gila?

297
00:15:02,900 --> 00:15:03,860
Saya rasional!

298
00:15:06,900 --> 00:15:07,940
Sebab saya tahu

299
00:15:08,380 --> 00:15:08,780
bahawa semua perkara

300
00:15:08,780 --> 00:15:09,660
di dunia ini pun

301
00:15:09,660 --> 00:15:10,940
tak setanding dengan awak.

